text: José Maurer (born 21 October 1951) is a Mexican equestrian. He competed in two events at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1951 births Category:Living people Category:Mexican male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Mexico Category:Equestrians at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
